original_title: The Very Best of WCW Monday Nitro Vol.3
overview: Nitro was WCW's flagship show for over 5 years, yielding over 500 hours of action-packed entertainment. Nitro Volumes 1 & 2 combined to showcase a multitude of classic moments. Volume 3 continues this series and this time, anything is possible!
title: The Very Best of WCW Monday Nitro Vol.3
